# Form & UI Kuralları

## React Hook Form + Zod
```typescript
const form = useForm<FormInput>({
  resolver: zodResolver(schema) as Resolver<FormInput>,
  defaultValues: { ... }
});
<Form form={form} onSubmit={form.handleSubmit(onSubmit)}>
```

## Form Bileşenleri
- `FormInput`, `FormSelect`, `FormSwitch`, `FormTextarea` — `components/forms/`
- `control={form.control}` ile bağla
- `disabled={form.formState.isSubmitting}` — submit sırasında devre dışı
- `required` prop ile zorunlu alan işareti

## Shadcn UI
- `components/ui/` — Card, Button, Input, Dialog, Select, Popover
- `cn()` ile class birleştir: `cn('base', condition && 'extra')`
- Tailwind ile stil; yeni bileşen eklerken `npx shadcn@latest add` kullan

## Form Card Yapısı
```tsx
<Card>
  <CardHeader className="sticky top-0 ...">
    <CardTitle>{pageTitle}</CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    <Form>...</Form>
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```
